      • getPropertiesFromTimestamp

        public Properties getPropertiesFromTimestamp(String group,
                                             long timestamp)
                                      throws SerialisationException
        Get the properties for a given group defined in the Schema as being stored in the HBase timestamp column.
        Parameters:
        group - The Element type to be queried
        timestamp - the element timestamp property
        Returns:
        The Properties stored within the Timestamp part of the Cell
        Throws:
        SerialisationException - If the supplied group has not been defined
